HEADWORD: Arabist
<hw>Ar`a*bist</hw> <pr>(<?/)</pr>, <pos>n.</pos> <ety>[Cf. F.
<ets>Arabiste</ets>.]</ety> <def>One well versed in the Arabic language
or literature; also, formerly, one who followed the Arabic system of
surgery.</def>⟦br⟧
